divs: Sighting DetailsWas walking next door to pick up our dog when i looked up in front of us there was a bright light and it was very big and bright at that time i told my girlfriend to go and get my camera she returned with it and the object did not move much so I started to take some pictures and tried to record it but the camera was having problems.So I told my girlfriend to keep an eye on it untill i returned with my video camera,tri-pod,and started to film as i was filming i was also taking pictures with the video camera while also using binoculars which made it a little closer I saw very bright white lights looked to be around 5 to 6 circular shape.I filmed for about 17 minutes it looked like it got closer and then move away untill it eventually went over the tree line and i couldn't see it anymore...
